data.description: *** FOR SALE OR TRADE! * Awesome Home Completely Remodeled So You Can Just Move-In! * HUGE PRICE ADJUSTMENT! * Features fig and avocado trees on the private backyard, vegetable beds, a tool shed/storage/studio/arts room * Close to Pittsburg Marina, shops, Old Downtown, restaurants, schools * One car garage with room for cars/RV/boat and toys inside gated driveway * Finished basement, may use as ADU, storage, recreational/study/music room * New 25 yr TPO (thermoplastic polyolefin) reflective roof * NEW: quick-lock flooring 100% water proof throughout, appliances, electrical, plumbing, new everything!!! * Most  pictures are virtually staged *** Home is eligible for a $17,500 grant to use for down payment & closing costs, lower interest rates, minimum FICO score of 620, must be your primary residence, no restrictions, 99% financing, no mortgage insurance, etc. Call Listing Agent for details *** As a VIP Buyer we can convert you to a Power Cash Buyer!!! Call Listing Agent for details *** Offers due Tuesday at 2pm *
